    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may require some routine maintenance and minor suspension work in the near future to get it back to its best. It is a solid, honest car that is priced according to its current state.",
